datasets.name: HPX Retention_CSS_Analytics
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', `First Device Event Date Time`) AS `month_first_device_event`, SUM(`Active_Devices`) AS `active_devices`, SUM(`Active_Devices`) / SUM(SUM(`Active_Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Months Since First Use` ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', `First Device Event Date Time`) ROWS UNBOUNDED PRECEDING) AS `percent_devices_returning` FROM `HPX Retention_CSS_Analytics` WHERE `First Device Event Date Time` >= '2023-05-01' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', `First Device Event Date Time`), `Months Since First Use` ORDER BY `month_first_device_event`
